::GoldenEye::

She was holding Dollen in her lap.  She looked up and around her.  
She heard yelling off in the distance. "HELP!  HELP UP PLEASE!"

She gently glided her hand over his face and looked at him,"Please 
wake up. Smile, frown, do something to know your alright."

She couldn't believe she was actually scared for this bot.  She found 
herself in a struggle with herself.  He had only met her a few weeks 
ago.  But she found her spark caring for him.  She was on the verge 
of tears with fright and worry for him.
